quran[23{c,v,t}:
51,52,"yuhin hota raha hai, inn se pehlay ki qomon ke paas bhi koi rasool aisa nahi aaya jisay unhon ne yeh nah kaha ho ke yeh sahir hai ya Majnoon"
51,53,"kya inn sab ne aapas mein iss par koi samjhota kar liya hai? nahi, balkeh yeh sab sarkash log hain"
51,54,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, un se rukh phair lau, tum par kuch malamat nahi"
51,55,"Albata nasiyaat karte raho, kyunkay nasiyaat imaan laane walon ke liye nafea hai"
51,56,mein ne jin aur insanon ko iss ke siwa kisi kaam ke liye peda nahi kya hai ke woh meri bandagi karen
51,57,mein unn se koi rizaq nahi chahta aur nah yeh chahta hon ke woh mujhe khilain
51,58,"Allah to khud hi Razzaq hai, barri qowat wala aur zabardast"
51,59,"pas jin logon ne zulm kya hai un ke hissay ka bhi waisa hi azaab tayyar hai jaissa aِnhi jaisay logon ko unn ke hissay ka mil chuka hai, is ke liye yeh log jaldi nah machayen"
51,60,aakhir ko tabahi hai kufar karne walon ke liye uss roz jis ka inhen khauf dilaya ja raha hai
52,1,qasam hai tor ki
52,2,aur aik aisi khuli kitaab ki
52,3,jo raqeeq jald mein likhi hui hai
52,4,aur abad ghar ki
52,5,aur onche chhat ki
52,6,aur mojzan samandar ki
52,7,ke tairay rab ka azaab zaroor waqay honay wala hai
52,8,jisay koi dafaa karne wala nahi
52,9,woh uss roz waqay hoga jab aasman buri terhan dagmagay ga
52,10,aur pahar uray uray phiren ge
52,11,tabahi hai uss roz unn jhutlanay walon ke liye
52,12,jo aaj khail ke tor par apni Hujjat bazyon mein lagey hue hain
52,13,jis din inhen dhakkay maar maar kar naar jahannum ki taraf le chala jaye ga
52,14,"uss waqt unn se kaha jaye ga ke"" yeh wohi aag hai jisay tum jhtlaya karte thay"
